          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi friends today I am gojng to share my views on SETH ANANDRAM JAIPURIA SCHOOL .\n\nFriends this school was founded by padmabhusan seth Mangturamji Jaipuria who wished the institution to grow into a centre of unbound academic excellence by fostering a spirit of multiculturalism.\n\nFriends the school has some very high qualified faculties and good administration staff.\n\nFriends the school has a vision to provide easy access to higher education with an array of varied subjects. To promote a mass approach to education by bringing within its fold students of all castes and to be at par with modern educational policies by laying emphasis on skill development and core values . friends the school has its vision in knowledge giving and not money earning\n\nHence parents should send their kids to this school\n\nThank you for reading my review\n\n￼",
