          "reviewBody": "Magnificent school with outstanding teachers. My child is studying in class 2 I and Ms. Neelam Bisht ma'am teaches Hindi. She is a very enthusiastic and polite teacher. She made a bond with the students and gave them support as per their requirement. Teachers like her are a pillar for the school. A big applaud for her👏👏👏👏",
