            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I want to congratulate director-principal ma'am Ms. Shalini Nambiar for these fantastic changes that she has brought to the school in this academic year. The improvements have been truly dramatic.👏👏. It is an awesome school with many extra-curricular activities for students. I also want to appreciate *Neelam Bisht ma'am*, the class teacher of class 2k. She is an excellent teacher full of knowledge, flexibility, patience and compassion. She makes the students engage with new learning opportunities.\nTeacher like her are an asset for the education system. I would like to request you to kindly promote her for grade 3 so that our children keep learning more things besides study. We will be obliged.",
